  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl whisk together matcha powder, lemon juice, olive oil, honey, salt, and pepper until smooth.",
    "Toss mixed greens in a large salad bowl.",
    "Add diced avocado, halved cherry tomatoes, sliced olives, and thinly sliced red onion to greens.",
    "Drizzle matcha vinaigrette over salad and toss gently to coat.",
    "Sprinkle crumbled feta cheese evenly across the salad.",
    "Add toasted pine nuts for crunch.",
    "Plate the salad on a chilled serving dish.",
    "Serve immediately while ingredients are fresh.",
    "Optionally garnish with extra matcha powder for visual appeal.",
    "Enjoy the velvety, pungent Croatian matcha salad."
